content.name: cdi_map_adm_address_guidewire_bronze_load

transformations.description: This source is designed to capture daily updates from the metal table and join with the target table to ensure that duplicate records are not loaded.
transformations.name: src_delta_changes_address_guidewire

object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)

SELECT DISTINCT
metal_aag.source_name, 
metal_aag.load_type,
metal_aag.address1,
metal_aag.address2,
metal_aag.agency_nup,
metal_aag.city,
metal_aag.country,
metal_aag.created,
metal_aag.id,
metal_aag.modified,
metal_aag.state,
metal_aag.type,
metal_aag.zip,
current_batch.batch_id
FROM $$raw_schema.adm_address_guidewire metal_aag
CROSS JOIN current_batch
ORDER BY 
metal_aag.agency_nup,
metal_aag.created,
metal_aag.modified;

'source_name' || source_name ||
'load_type' || load_type ||
'address1' || address1 ||
'address2' || address2 ||
'agency_nup' || o_agency_nup ||
'city' || city ||
'country' || country ||
'created' || o_created ||
'id' || o_id ||
'modified' || o_modified ||
'state' || state ||
'type' || type ||
'zip' || zip
)
